  dialogPieces:
  - ID: Noah
    image: {fileID: 0}
    text: The accident was just that.
  - ID: Noah
    image: {fileID: 0}
    text: This wasn't because of you.
  - ID: Noah
    image: {fileID: 0}
    text: "It wasn\u2019t because of me."
  - ID: Noah
    image: {fileID: 0}
    text: "She didn\u2019t leave because of me."
  - ID: Noah
    image: {fileID: 0}
    text: "But why do I still feel\u2026"
  - ID: Noah
    image: {fileID: 0}
    text: like I failed to hold onto her?
